title: 6 coaches of Jabalpur-Mahakoshal Express derail near Mahoba in Uttar Pradesh
text:
6 coaches of Jabalpur-Mahakoshal Express derail in UP, rescue operations on Six coaches of Mahakoshal Express derailed on the stretch betwen Kulpahar and Mahoba in Uttar Pradesh. IndiaToday.in | Written by Shraddha Jandial A + A - 
Six coaches of Mahakoshal Express derailed on the stretch betwen Kulpahar and Mahoba in Uttar Pradesh. 
Three AC coaches and three general coaches of the Mahakoshal Express, that runs between Jabalpur and New Delhi derailed aruound 2.30 am Thursday morning. 
So far, 10 people have been reported to be injured and rushed to the nearby hospital. 
Railway police and officials are at the spot and rescue operations are on.
